the last line by the Frenet-Serret for formula *planar* curves which show $\vec{T}'(s) = \kappa(s) \vec{N}$ and $\vec{N}'(s) = -\kappa(s)\vec{T}(s)$.

To compute the curvature of $\vec\beta_a$, we need to compute both:

$$~
